▼作者|翟耀媛新冠疫情治疗药物尚未明确之下，A股在2月3日新春开市以来，一大批疫情概念股搭上“便车”，跨界经营。
A large number of conceptual stocks have hitched up to cross border operations since February 3, when the Chinese New Year opened, because of uncertainty about what to do with the new crown.
其中口罩、消毒剂、医疗器械等概念股集体迎来小高潮，相关个股市值大増。
Among them mask, disinfectant, medical equipment and other conceptual shares welcomed a small climax, the relevant stocks market value increased.
而在经历数日涨停后，疫情概念股近期纷纷下行降温。
And after a few days of trading, the epidemic concept of the recent decline in the cooling.
清流工作室发现，2月5日以来，多只热门题材个股收到深交所关注函。
Clearing Studio found that since February 5, a number of hot topics have received the attention of the Shenzhen Stock Exchange letter.
上市公司“跨界营业”疫情爆发至今，不断有上市公司跨界生产疫情防控物资。
Listed companies "cross-border business" outbreak so far, listed companies continue to produce cross-border epidemic prevention and control materials.
以口罩为例，网易清流工作室不完全统计，1月1日至2月14日期间，至少33家A股上市公司跨界生产口罩，主要通过车间转产医用、投资设计医疗器械子公司等方式，投入到口罩产能转化中。
Taking masks as an example, Netease Flow Clearing Studio is not fully statistics. Between January 1 and February 14, at least 33 A-share listed companies produced masks across the border, mainly through workshops, investment in the design of medical equipment subsidiary companies, etc., into the transformation of mask production capacity.
其中几大巨头包括中国石化（600028.SH）、工业富联(601138.SH)等。
Some of these giants include Sinopec (600028.SH) and the Industrial Rich Alliance (601138.SH).
2月6日，中国石化在其官方微博上发布求助信息：公司有原料熔喷布，亟需口罩机增产口罩抗击疫情。
On Feb. 6, Sinopec posted a call for help on its official microblog, saying it needed a mask machine to boost production to combat the epidemic.
若有富余、可用的设备，可转让给中国石化，公司将协调生产、增产口罩。
If surplus and usable equipment can be transferred to Sinopec, the company will coordinate the production and production of face masks.
此外，中国石化本月还将加紧生产近10万吨聚丙烯、合成树脂等医卫原料。
In addition, Sinopec will step up production of nearly 100,000 tons of polypropylene, synthetic resin and other medical materials this month.
网易清流工作室此前曾接触中石化人员，对方称，中石化将整合各方资源，发挥央企的调动能力，通过购买口罩机、收购口罩商或者帮助口罩商调配原材料、申请医疗资质等方式，尽快帮助口罩商恢复产能。
Netease clean-up studio had previously contacted Sinopec staff, which said Sinopec would pool its resources to tap the ability of central companies to help mask makers restore capacity as soon as possible by buying masks, buying masks dealers or helping mask makers to allocate raw materials and apply for medical qualifications.
富士康2月6日表示，集团旗下工业富联近日在集团龙华园区首次导入口罩生产线，并于2月5日顺利实现试产，目前，正在申请产品资质认证中。
Foxconn said on February 6, the group's industrial rich union in the Group's Longhua Park for the first time into the production line, and February 5, a successful trial production, is now applying for product certification.
同时，富士康表示，相关产能预计在2月底可达到日产200万只。
Meanwhile, Foxconn said capacity was expected to reach 2m a day by the end of February.
除了口罩这一高频词汇，消毒剂、防护服等疫情刚需也成为行业热点。
In addition to the high-frequency mask vocabulary, disinfectant, protective clothing and other epidemics have just become hot spots in the industry.
网易清流工作室不完全统计，1月1日至2月14日期间，加入消毒剂、防护服生产的A股上市公司分别有15家、11家，其中部分企业为应急生产或临时生产。
According to incomplete statistics, from January 1 to February 14, 15 companies listed on A-share joined in the production of disinfectants and protective clothing. Some of these companies were engaged in emergency production or temporary production.
上述企业中，紫鑫药业（002118.SZ）、陇神戎发（300534.SZ）同时生产口罩、消毒剂、防护服三种设备；延安必康（002411.SZ）同时生产口罩和消毒剂；红豆股份(600400.SH)、搜于特（002503.SZ）、佛慈制药（002644.SZ）、龙头股份（600630.SH）、华纺股份（600448.SH）、华软科技（002453.SZ）和华升股份（600156.SH）共7家公司同时加入口罩和防护服的生产。
Among these enterprises, Xin Pharmaceutical (002118.SZ), Longshen Rongshen (300534.SZ) simultaneously produce three kinds of masks, disinfectants and protective clothing; Yanan Beikang (002411.SZ), Soybean Shares (002503.SZ), Fotz Pharmaceutical (002643.SH), Huaxin Technology (002448.SH), Huashen Technology (002448.SH) and Huasheng (600156.SH).
股市之外，投入口罩生产的企业数量更是激增。
Outside the stock market, the number of companies investing in mask production has soared.
据新京报智库统计，全国只有559个医用口罩类许可证，分别为353家企业所持有。
According to the Beijing News think tank, there are only 559 medical masks in China, held by 353 enterprises.
而天眼查统计数据显示，1月1日至2月7日间，超过3000家企业新增了“口罩、防护服、消毒液、测温仪、医疗器械”等经营范围。
From January 1 to February 7, more than 3,000 companies added "masks, protective clothing, disinfectant, thermometers, medical devices" to their operations, according to sky-eye statistics.
许多企业“跨界”进入医疗器械行业，零售业、批发业、商业服务、科技推广等都成为热门“跨界“行业。
Many companies "cross-border" into the medical device industry, retail trade, wholesale trade, business services, technology promotion and other popular "cross-border" industries.
它们当中，注册资本低于100万元的小微企业占比达38%，超过一半的企业注册资本低于500万元。
Among them, micro and small enterprises with a registered capital of less than 1 million yuan account for 38%, and more than half of them have a registered capital of less than 5 million yuan.
上市公司中，大幅度“跨界”加入疫情防控设备生产的企业不在少数。
Listed companies, a large number of "cross-border" into the production of equipment for disease control and prevention.
2月13日，中顺洁柔全资子公司取得应急医疗器械生产凭证。
Feb. 13, Zhongshun Jairou wholly-owned subsidiary obtained the certificate of production of emergency medical equipment.
据网易清流工作室不完全统计，此前，汽车企业上汽集团（600104.SH）、广汽集团（601238.SH）、比亚迪（002594.SZ），纺织服装企业搜于特、华纺股份、龙头股份、红豆股份、水星家纺（603365.SH）、报喜鸟（002154.SZ）、柏堡龙（002776.SZ），工业电子企业中国石化、富士康、长盈精密（300115.SZ）、首航高科（002665.SZ）、赢合科技（300457.SZ）等企业，以及爹地宝贝（834683）和格力地产（600185.SH），累计17家上市公司跨界投入医疗器械生产当中。
Before that, SAIC (6000104.SH), Guangqi Group (601238.SH), BYD (002594.SZ), textile and apparel companies such as Suntech, China Textile, Leading Shares, Red Bean Stock, Mercury Home Textile (603365.SH), Winehouse Technology (002154.SZ), Berkeley (002776.SZ), Industrial Electronics Company China Petrochemical Company (002154.SZ), Winning Technology (002776.SZ), Industrial Electronics Company China Petrochemical Company (002154.SZ), Winning Technology (002776.SZ), Industrial Electronics Company China Petrochemical Company (002154.SZ), Winning Technology (002776.SZ), Industrial Electronics Company China Petrochemical Company (002154.SZ), Winning Technology (00
多只概念股收“关注函”在搭上疫情“便车”的路途中，多只个股并非一帆风顺。
A number of conceptual stocks received "letter of concern" on the way to the epidemic "hitchhiking," many stocks are not plain sailing.
网易清流工作室统计，2月5日至2月14日间，深交所共发出13份疫情相关的关注函及问询函，占此期间发函总数的约30%。
Between February 5 and February 14, the Shenzhen Stock Exchange issued 13 epidemic-related letters of concern and letters of enquiry, accounting for about 30% of the total number of communications sent during the period, according to the Netease Clearing Studio.
在这13份函件中，病毒抑制药物相关4份，口罩生产相关3份，消毒剂相关2份，医疗器械相关1份，在线教育相关3份。
Of the 13 communications, 4 were related to viral drugs, 3 to mask production, 2 to disinfectants, 1 to medical devices and 3 to online education.
值得注意的是，收到问询函的均为在线教育企业。
It is worth noting that the inquiries were received by online educational enterprises.
在疫情期间“停课不停学”的影响下，世纪天鸿（300654.SZ）、全通教育（300359.SZ）和方直科技（300235.SZ），均因股价涨幅较大、达到异动标准而收到问询函。
Under the influence of "non-stop learning" during the epidemic, Centuries Tianhong (300654.SZ), Quan Tong Education (300359.SZ) and Founder Technology (300235.SZ) all received inquiries because of the large increase in share prices and the achievement of different standards.
2月5日，深交所针对疫情概念股发出第一份关注函，指向自称生产病毒抑制药物关键中间体的雅本化学（300261.SZ）。
On 5 February, the Shenzhen Stock Exchange sent its first letter of concern to the conceptual unit of the outbreak, pointing to the Yabun chemistry (300261.SZ), which claims to be a key intermediate in the production of viral inhibitors.
关注函显示，雅本化学于2月4日在互动易平台表示，其子公司为药物达芦那韦关键中间体的主要供应商，2月5日公司股价即涨停。
According to the letter of concern, Arbor Chemistry said on Feb. 4 at InteractivePlatform that its subsidiary was the main supplier of the drug Daruinawa key intermediates and that its stock price rose and fell on February 5.
深交所要求公司说明是否存在主动迎合市场热点、炒作公司股价的情形。
Shenzhen Stock Exchange asked the company to explain whether there are active to meet market hot spots, speculation in the company's share price.
2月6日，泰和科技（300801.SZ）收到深交所发出的第一份消毒剂相关的关注函。
On 6 February, Tai Wo Technology (300801.SZ) received the first disinfectant-related letter of concern from the Shenzhen Stock Exchange.
关注函指出，泰和科技公开表示能够生产病毒防疫所用的环境消毒产品，且于2月3日披露拟将过氧乙酸等加入经营范围，2月4日至6日股票连续涨停。
The letter of concern noted that Taichung had publicly stated that it was in a position to produce environmental disinfection products for viral prophylaxis and had disclosed on February 3 that it intended to include peroxyacetic acid in its operations.
深交所要求其说明产品生产条件等信息。
The Shenzhen Stock Exchange requires it to specify production conditions and other information.
2月8日，正业科技（300410.SZ）公开称，公司正组织N95口罩和平面口罩设备生产，2月10日至12日股价连续涨停。
On February 8, Zhengye Technology (300410.SZ) announced that it was organizing the production of N95 masks and planar mask equipment.
深交所向其发出关注函，要求说明设备具体研发情况、是否存在炒作情形等。
The Shenzhen Stock Exchange sent a letter of concern to it, asking for specific research and development of equipment, whether there is speculation, and so on.
值得注意的是，上述13家收函企业均属于中小企业板和创业板。
It is worth noting that the 13 above-mentioned enterprises are small and medium-sized enterprises board and GEM.
而疫情之下，表现出彩的稳健医疗正预备冲击IPO。
And under the epidemic, the display of robust medical care is preparing to hit IPOs.
公司官网显示，1月10日起，稳健医疗黄冈分公司即开始不休假生产N95口罩、外科口罩和护理口罩。
Since January 10, the company's Huanggang branch began to take no vacation to produce N95 masks, surgical masks and nursing masks, according to the company's website.
自2019年12月20日至2020年1月26日，稳健医疗共向医院、药店、电商供应上亿只口罩，向医院供应11万余件防护服。
From December 20, 2019 to January 26, 2020, Stable Medicine supplied hundreds of millions of masks to hospitals, pharmacies, and electricity companies, and more than 110,000 protective suits to hospitals.
今年1月3日，稳健医疗既2005年首次试图上市后，再次冲击IPO，拟登陆创业板。
On January 3, 2005, Healthcare tried to go public for the first time after the IPO, to hit IPO, to be landing on the GEM.
翟耀媛是清流工作室研究助理，常驻北京。
Zhai Yaofu is a research assistant in Qingliu Studio based in Beijing.
